Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:36.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is motion sickness...\Nno, Yutaka Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Today we're taking a school trip to Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since I like looking at old temples and castles,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:46.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to\N go to Kyushu, where Dazaifu is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been training hard for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I tried getting in a stopped car
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and watching moving trains\Nat the bullet train platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:58.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everything was perfect and\Nthere wasn't even one oversight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I didn't even imagine\N we'd be taking an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, brother, isn't it too difficult for us\Nto do something like hijacking after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's with you, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:12.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really worried because\Nit was a high school field trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but they all look like yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:18.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Certainly, it's almost making me\Nfeel like we're the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's just quit now. We haven't done\Nanything yet, so we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Were they going to hijack\N the plane that we were going to board?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:30.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's a huge crime! \NI can't let them do it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if they actually commit the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,our school trip will probably be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Which means the plane may not take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's actually fortunate for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, that's not good! They may just go ahead\Nand decide not to hijack the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I can't act in a way that \Nmay encourage them to hijack the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm a badass,\N I'm not rotten enough to assist in a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:52.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After all, as a citizen,\N I should pray that they don't commit a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, then let's hijack the plane\Nafter it takes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:56.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:57.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "huh?", dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,From how your conversation was going,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:03.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you should've mended your ways and\Ndecided not to hijack the plane, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:07.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry. To tell you the truth,\N this is my first time getting on a plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so I panicked a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:12.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Same here. I certainly\Nunderstand your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you\N calm down first and talk it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:20.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I'm no good when lots of people\Nare around, because I get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If it's possible, I'd like to have a meeting\Nwhere only a few people are around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay! Everyone, go home, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Then what's gonna happen\Nto the school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you don't go home right away,\NI'll fudging kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I feel better, since there are only\Na few people around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You get timid in front of strangers, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I should've gone home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel reassured if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right! If we listen to\Nwhat he's saying, we're invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now I don't feel like canceling our plan at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:51.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Damn! It looks as if I've become their\Naccomplice somewhere along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I told them to bring us two billion yen and fly the plane to the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They said okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No way! Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You skipped too much of the conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:05.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm getting really sick.\N Why in the hell am I on a plane to the US?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our boss looks somewhat blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not your boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Yutaka Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no one who's stronger at fighting\Nor more reliable than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was the boss at a certain school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But that story's in the past now.
