Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:28.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Where the hell does this road go to?\NAnd where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've come to the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here I shall gain a strong body\N that can ride any transportation with ease,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and go back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, I imagine\N they're all in an uproar in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fs32\pos(530.203,451)\blur0.5}Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard it was really awful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,having trouble with hijackers\N instead of taking a school trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:50.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,although I don't know many details,\Nsince I wasn't there due to my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it was good that no one got hurt\Nand everyone was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But don't you feel like we're\Nforgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:01.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know it sounds strange\N for me to say this since I wasn't there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but aren't you all forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We haven't gotten the money\Nfor the school trip back yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's it!
