Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:13.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess the whole school must be\Ntalking about me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess the whole school must be\Ntalking about me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for me to feel this lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I wonder if those hijackers\Nwere able to escape okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it was hard to dislike those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How beautiful the stars are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:39.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my friends in Japan\N are also watching the same stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:50.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\bord30\shad0\c&H1D2324&\3c&HE7F0F1&\blur0.4\frz272\b0\fs36\clip(491,97,538,329)\pos(503.013,210)}J{\frz271}a{\frz270}p{\frz268.5}a{\frz268}n {\frz268}(1 p{\frz267.5}m)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:50.83,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\bord10\shad0\c&H1D2324&\3c&HE7F0F1&\blur1\frz277\b0\fs8\pos(166.538,172)\clip(m 163.125 148 l 166.5 196 179 197 174.5 147)}J{\frz274}a{\frz273}p{\frz272}a{\frz272.5}n {\frz274}(1 p{\frz274.5}m)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:50.95,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\bord10\shad0\c&H1D2324&\3c&HE7F0F1&\blur1\frz277\b0\fs8\pos(186.93,170)\frx2\fry20\clip(m 183.5 146 l 188.125 193 198.25 194 192.625 144)}J{\frz274}a{\frz273}p{\frz272}a{\frz272.5}n {\frz274}(1 p{\frz274.5}m)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, there's a time difference\Nbetween Japan and the US,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so even if it's nighttime in the US,\Nit's daytime in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So when Americans are watching stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Japanese people are taking naps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why do you say stuff like that out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And besides, everyone knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, I wanted to brag that\Neven I know about astronomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:04.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's important right now is whether\Nwe'll get a refund for the trip or not, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:09.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I only got half back for the cancellation,\Nbecause it was due to my cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You canceled\N because of your own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just half, be thankful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:17.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But in our case, they cancelled it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's only right to give us the entire amount back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Instead of "they," it was\N because of hijackers, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel like we're forgetting\Nsomething more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is there something that we're\Nforgetting, Takenouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:30.91,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\b0\blur0.4\c&H282C2D&\fnThe Rifleman\frz-8\pos(-5.665,129)}Take
