Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:31.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is there something that we're\Nforgetting, Takenouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, it's business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's something that I really want to say,\Nbut I wonder if it's okay to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble!\N Maeda got caught by Bass High again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:45.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Give me a break! How many times\Ndoes he have to get caught?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:50.47,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Shinjiro Hayashida
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been attracting any attention lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}so he may be trying to get some\Nattention in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case, we'd better rescue him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That means a battle with Bass High, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:07:00.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But Bass guys are really tough,\Nso we should be well prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:05.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're picking a fight with Cro-High,\Nso they must have enough guys for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We haven't had a fight this big in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Certainly, it may become\Na very dangerous battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Main character Takashi Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Because we have Takenouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:12.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\b0\blur0.4\c&H282C2D&\fnThe Rifleman\fs16\pos(3.399,250)}Take
