Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. I feel like the situation\Nhas become irreversible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been pretending to be a high school\Nstudent to avoid arrest,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I didn't know, of all those people,\Nhe was the toughest boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have to somehow\Nfast-talk my way out of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,although I get terrified around strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:37.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing how many\NTakenouchi will fudgin' kill today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:46.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're already sixteen.\NAge-wise we may still be children,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:49.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but wouldn't now be a good time\Nto become independent adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're too old to be fighting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why don't you become adults now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And what I'm afraid of the most is the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:03.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I get caught by them because of\Na stupid fight like this, it wouldn't be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course, everyone is afraid of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you're afraid, you can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You really don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's a big difference between you\Ngetting caught and me getting caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't tell you the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but if I get caught now, I'll spend\Nat least twenty years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,T-Twenty years?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:27.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you have a serious\Ncriminal record at the age of 16?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I knew you were different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're still young and have a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to spend\Na worthless life like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Takenouchi, you've changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Your way of thinking is like\Nsomeone in his thirties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's as if you're a different man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or more like, aren't you a different person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, people have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:52.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if you take fighting away from us,\Nthere's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When I was in a Mexican prison, long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:56.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Seriously? When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:02.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was locked up in a small cell for days\Nand there was nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:05.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moreover, I was imprisoned\Nalthough I was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After twenty days or so,\NI was already mentally distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:15.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,While in that state, I found a pair of puzzle rings\Nwhen I looked at one corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:20.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was so upset that I tried to\N detach them with all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:24.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But the more power I put into it,\Nthe harder it got to detach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't need power to detach puzzle rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:30.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What you need is a little trick and a calm mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:35.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I realized it after struggling with\Nthe puzzle rings for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:40.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I easily detached the puzzle rings that\NI couldn't detach with all my might before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The puzzle rings healed my dissolute mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A few days later, the trial was held,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and my innocence was validated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These are the puzzle rings from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Those are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How about it? Try to detach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They don't move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't do it. They don't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:10.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Your minds have grown wild like animals,\Nsince all you guys do every day is fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:16.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And those puzzle rings can't be detached\N unless you have a decent and calm human mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow! They came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? I didn't realize that there was someone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who had a decent human mind\Namong such savage guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:32.15,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Bass High School
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:32.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Your friends never come to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that you don't have any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but even if I don't invite them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they all always come to my house to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're doing it to annoy me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.04,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Akira Maeda
