Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The cold season has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of yourself and\Nsleep warm so that you won't get a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Brush your teeth, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:49.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(181.266,360)}Is the US a place that you can't\N live without transportation?!
